On one side I want to take on 2 or 3 stem courses that I need to take but that won't give me 12 units to be full-time. So I'm in between and it gets hard sometimes.

When the campus is opened, I already moved to Hemet, CA so not that convenient to just stop by so I'm not in any club or organization.  The tutoring services were not as good as it used to be and last semester was a disappointment so I chose not to use the services this semester.
